[20.20 May 4: Circuit Breaker Day #28] Cannot decide between Laksa Yong Tau Foo or Curry Chicken Mee? Cook myself and I get both! 😂

Ingredients:
Yong Tau Foo and Thick beehoon, one whole toasted chicken from @coldstoragesg
@primataste Laksa premix
Water to dilute
Frozen shrimps
Parsley flakes (optional)
Water to dilute

Everything goes into #NinjaFoodiOP300,

Air-fried the YTF first then sautée mode, to bring the premix, paste and water to boil, pour over noodles and serve.
